title: CPA Workout II
description:
This is a follow-up video for CPA I (see my uploads).

A Miami Beach fitness trainer created what he calls the "CPA" workout (cardio/plyometric/aerobic). This is a set of exercises that uses a suspension trainer, but otherwise requires no extra equipment or gym facilities (everything can be done on a playground or park). This is a great way to get outside and enjoy the nice weather while you get in shape.

The exercises are explained and demonstrated to make sure you are doing them correctly. If you like this video, check out my other uploads to add more exercises to this kind of workout.
